```

This additional check ensures that the target height doesn't exceed the screen height. If it does, it adjusts the target height and width accordingly to fit within the screen. The xOffset is recalculated to center the viewport horizontally.

By adding this check, the code should prevent the viewport from being moved too far offscreen and disappearing when the screen's aspect ratio is smaller than the desired aspect ratio.

